# Production-Grade Test Module — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

14 new/modified files, 1,591 lines of code committed to `main` (commit `478fcf1`).

---

## 1. Data Layer — 3 New Models

| File | Model | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| [src/models/Test.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Test.ts) | [ProTest](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Test.ts#27-46) | Replaces old flat schema. Supports sections, batch/subject filter, negative marking, shuffle, resultMode |
| [src/models/TestAnswerKey.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/TestAnswerKey.ts) | [TestAnswerKey](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/TestAnswerKey.ts#12-18) | **Separate collection** — never returned to students. Stores correct answers + reasons |
| [src/models/TestAttempt.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/TestAttempt.ts) | [ProTestAttempt](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/TestAttempt.ts#21-44) | Rich attempt record: raw answers + graded answers + negative marks + per-student `resultVisible` flag |

---

## 2. JSON Schema Validator

[src/lib/testSchemaValidator.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/testSchemaValidator.ts)

- [validateQuestionsFile()](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/testSchemaValidator.ts#63-130) — strict structural check, duplicate `questionId` detection, 4-option enforcement
- [validateAnswersFile()](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/testSchemaValidator.ts#131-182) — cross-references every `questionId` with questions.json, warns on missing answers
- Returns typed `{ valid, errors[], warnings[] }` — no throwing

---

## 3. Admin APIs

| Route | Method | Description |
|---|---|---|
| [/api/admin/tests](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/tests) | GET | Lists tests, attempt counts, populated batch/subject |
| [/api/admin/tests](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/tests) | POST | Dual JSON upload → validate → save ProTest + TestAnswerKey atomically |
| `/api/admin/tests/[id]` | GET | Test detail + leaderboard-sorted attempts |
| `/api/admin/tests/[id]` | PATCH | Toggle [isActive](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/layout/Sidebar.tsx#85-86) |
| `/api/admin/tests/[id]` | DELETE | Cascade deletes test + answer key + all attempts |
| `/api/admin/tests/[id]/publish` | PATCH | Sets `isPublished = true` on test, `resultVisible = true` on all attempts |

---

## 4. Student APIs

| Route | Method | Description |
|---|---|---|
| [/api/student/tests](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/tests) | GET | Only returns tests matching student's batch |
| `/api/student/tests/[id]` | GET | Questions without answers. Applies shuffle if configured. Enforces batch match |
| `/api/student/tests/[id]` | POST | Grades submission with negative marking. Returns full result (instant) or acknowledgement (manual) |
| `/api/student/tests/[id]/result` | GET | Returns graded answers if `resultVisible`. Returns pending message if not yet published |

---

## 5. Teacher Dashboard ([TestManager.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/TestManager.tsx))

- Drag-and-drop file pickers for `questions.json` + `answers.json`
- Live validation error display + warnings block
- Inline JSON format reference (`<details>` expandable)
- Test list with status/mode/published badges
- Collapsible **leaderboard** per test (sorted by marks)
- **Publish Results** button for manual-mode tests
- Toggle active/inactive + delete with cascade warning

---

## 6. Student UI

### Test List Page ([/student/tests](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/tests))
- Stats bar: Total / Pending / Completed / Avg%
- Circular SVG performance gauge for overall score
- Filter tabs: All / Pending / Done
- Cards show: subject, duration, questions, marks, neg marking, result mode
- Score bar + correct/wrong/skip counts for completed tests
- "Awaiting publication" state for manual-mode tests

### Test-Taking Page (`/student/tests/[id]`)
- **Sticky timer** with colour-coded progress bar (green→yellow→red, pulse at 30 sec)
- **Question palette** — green (answered), orange (flagged), white (unanswered)
- **Flag for review** button (🚩) per question
- Section group headings with instructions
- Per-question marks visible `[2M]`
- Prev/Next navigation inside each question card
- Timer initialised once from `useEffect([test])` — **no restart bug**
- Auto-submit on timer expiry

### Result Page (`/student/tests/[id]/result`)
- **Manual pending state** — clean "⏳ Result Pending" screen, no score shown
- **Instant / published** — gradient scorecard (green/yellow/red by score)
- 4-stat grid: marks, correct, wrong, skipped
- Negative marks deduction note
- Collapsible answer review per question:
  - Student answer vs correct answer
  - `marksAwarded` (can be negative)
  - 💡 Teacher-written explanation (reason)

---

## Security

- Answer key stored in **separate [TestAnswerKey](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/TestAnswerKey.ts#12-18) collection** — never queried from student-facing routes
- Batch filter on both list and individual test fetch — students can't access other batches' tests
- Re-submission blocked at DB level (unique index `{ testId, studentId }`)
- Result visibility controlled by `resultVisible` flag on each attempt, not just test metadata
